description: Inspired by the sausages of Calabria in Southern Italy that are among the oldest and most traditional in the region. These fiery, spiced sausages are filled with coarse ground Sow Stall Free Australian Pork, and seasoned with paprika, fennel and chilli for a rich, bold taste with a kick.
name: Calabrese Sausages
